                <h1>When Did The Brady Bunch Premiere?</h1>
                <p>The Brady Bunch premiered on September 26, 1969. This beloved series, created by Sherwood Schwartz, followed the lives of a blended family, the Bradys, and their trials and tribulations of cohabitation. The show became iconic for its portrayal of family dynamics and remains a staple of American pop culture.</p>
